文章二
来自：Impact of early events and lifestyle on the gut microbiota and metabolic phenotypes in young school-age children. micorbiome. 2019方法：DMM, PAM-JSD, PAM-BC描述：Genus-level enterotypes analysis was performed according to the Dirichlet multinomial mixtures (DMM) and partitioning around medoid (PAM)-based clustering protocols using Jensen-Shannon divergence (PAM-JSD) and Bray-Curtis (PAM-BC)

